FBIS4-3993 "drchi082_b_94005" FBIS-CHI-94-082 Daily Report 26 Apr 1994 United States & Canada Leaders' Activities, Reaction To Honor Former President Nixon Leaders' Activities, Reaction To Honor Former President Nixon Zou Jiahua To Attend Funeral OW2604132394 Beijing XINHUA in English 1313 GMT 26 Apr 94 OW2604132394 Beijing XINHUA English BFN [Text] Beijing, April 26 (XINHUA) -- The Chinese Government has decided to entrust vice-premier of the State Council Zou Jiahua to attend the funeral of former U.S. President Richard Milhous Nixon in California of the United States.
